title: How to use Pinecone for vector search?
text: Pinecone is a fully managed vector database that makes it easy to add vector search to your applications. It allows you to store and search high-dimensional vectors efficiently.

title: Understanding Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
text: Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) is a framework that combines retrieval of relevant documents with a generative model to produce more accurate and informative responses.

title: Best practices for implementing QA systems
text: To implement an effective QA system, ensure that your training data is diverse and representative, and always evaluate model performance with real user queries.
